commits.message:
Added intelligent shooting

Cant shoot behind back. Has to be within line of sight

Updated other files - added spell script

Fireballs now no longer come from the wizards nose

Quality of life improvements

Added attack animation. Tweaked attack animation so it could be used as a valid logic gate.

Updated health/mana bar

Made it so that the number changes when the bar does
Added functionality for changing health/mana bar

New Class

Needed to keep track of character stats

New Documentation

Cleaned up character class with more precise documentation

Character Movement

Learned how to remove sprites, as well as have them change face while they're moving
